---
const effectiveDate = "June 17, 2026";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Privacy policy for JXC Global."
    />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml" />
    <title>Privacy Policy | JXC</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light;
        --black: #000;
        --white: #fff;
        --muted: #555;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html {
        font-family:
          Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
          "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        background: var(--white);
        color: var(--black);
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-width: 320px;
      }

      a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .shell {
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-rows: auto 1fr auto;
      }

      header,
      footer {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 16px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        padding: 20px clamp(18px, 4vw, 56px);
        border-bottom: 2px solid var(--black);
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 800;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      footer {
        border-top: 2px solid var(--black);
        border-bottom: 0;
        padding-block: 18px;
      }

      .brand {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 800;
      }

      main {
        padding: clamp(42px, 7vw, 92px) clamp(18px, 5vw, 72px);
      }

      .content {
        max-width: 900px;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 18px;
        font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 116px);
        line-height: 0.9;
        letter-spacing: 0;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .date {
        margin: 0 0 48px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 750;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      h2 {
        margin: 42px 0 12px;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.2;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      p,
      li {
        font-size: clamp(17px, 2vw, 20px);
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      p {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
      }

      ul {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        padding-left: 24px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 680px) {
        header,
        footer {
          align-items: flex-start;
          flex-direction: column;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="shell">
      <header>
        <a class="brand" href="/">JXC</a>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
      </header>

      <main>
        <article class="content">
          <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
          <p class="date">Effective {effectiveDate}</p>

          <p>
            JOC Exploration &amp; Cattle LLC operates the JXC website. This
            Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information
            when you visit this website or contact us.
          </p>

          <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>
            We may collect information you choose to provide, such as your name,
            email address, company, and message content when you contact us.
          </p>
          <p>
            We may also receive basic technical information from your browser or
            device, such as IP address, browser type, referring page, pages
            visited, and timestamps.
          </p>

          <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>To respond to inquiries and communicate with you.</li>
            <li>To operate, maintain, and improve the website.</li>
            <li>To understand website usage and diagnose technical issues.</li>
            <li>To protect the website and prevent misuse.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Cookies and Analytics</h2>
          <p>
            The website may use cookies or similar technologies for basic site
            functionality, analytics, or performance measurement. You can adjust
            cookie settings through your browser.
          </p>

          <h2>Sharing Information</h2>
          <p>
            We do not sell personal information. We may share information with
            service providers who help us operate the website or communicate with
            you, or when required by law.
          </p>

          <h2>Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            We keep information only as long as reasonably necessary for the
            purposes described in this policy, unless a longer retention period
            is required or permitted by law.
          </p>

          <h2>Security</h2>
          <p>
            We use reasonable administrative, technical, and organizational
            measures to protect information. No method of transmission or storage
            is completely secure.
          </p>

          <h2>Your Choices</h2>
          <p>
            You may contact us to request access, correction, or deletion of
            personal information you have provided, subject to legal and
            operational requirements.
          </p>

          <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Updates will be
            posted on this page with a revised effective date.
          </p>

          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For privacy questions, contact us at
            <a href="mailto:hello@jxc.global">hello@jxc.global</a>.
          </p>
        </article>
      </main>

      <footer>
        <span>&copy; JOC Exploration &amp; Cattle LLC</span>
        <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
